overview:
Entity formation (corporation and limited liability company (LLC)), document retrieval and registered agent services in all 50 states, plus Washington, D.C. Headquartered in Boston, Massachusetts, CFS (www.FilingsMadeEasy.com) assists entrepreneurs and professionals (lawyers, paralegals and accounting firms) with filing and registered agent services.

Corporations and LLCs (and other business entities) are designed to protect the business owners’ personal assets (by providing limited liability protections), and are common vehicles used in the United States for many types of organizations. CFS assists with obtaining FEIN (tax identification number), s-corporation elections, 83(b) elections, registered agent services, document retrieval (such as good standing certificates or certified charters) throughout the United States.
